➜IBM和甲骨文合作开发OpenJDK
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=20448	17280
IBM<a href="http://www.marketwire.com/press-release/Oracle-and-IBM-Collaborate-to-Accelerate-Java-Innovation-Through-OpenJDK-NASDAQ-ORCL-1332855.htm">宣布</a>它将与甲骨文公司合作开发OpenJDK Java环境，<a href="http://lwn.net/Articles/409579/">加快Java平台创新</a>。<i>
